item.title: Server help please
item.dc:creator: @luna-scape luna-scape
item.description:
@luna-scape wrote:

go to ur commands.java search like givemod or only give or playerrights w/e
U will find commands from how to make sumone ranked.

Probably it is:
givemod (playername)
giveadmin (playername)
giveowner (playername)
givedonor (playername)

if this doesnt work u probably didnt make urself main owner.
